    "ST x (¬φ) = ∀y(y ⊑ x → ¬ST y (φ)), where y is a fresh variable;3.",
    "ST x ((φ ∧ ψ)) = (ST x (φ) ∧ ST x (ψ)); 4.",
    "ST x ((φ → ψ)) = ∀y((y ⊑ x ∧ ST y (φ)) → ST y (ψ)), where y is a fresh variable;5.",
    "ST x (□ i φ) = ∀y(x Ṙi y → ST y (φ)), where y is a fresh variable.Let ST (φ) = ∀xST x (φ).",
    "◁ Proposition 6.10 (Correspondence on Models)."
